## Project Structure (Monorepo)

```
waqup-new/
├── packages/
│   ├── shared/              # Shared code (business logic)
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── services/   # API services (Supabase)
│   │   │   ├── stores/     # Zustand stores
│   │   │   ├── types/      # TypeScript types
│   │   │   ├── utils/      # Utilities
│   │   │   └── schemas/    # Zod validation schemas
│   │   ├── package.json
│   │   └── tsconfig.json
│   │
│   ├── mobile/              # React Native app (Android + iOS)
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── app/        # App entry
│   │   │   ├── screens/    # Screen components
│   │   │   ├── components/ # React Native components
│   │   │   ├── navigation/ # React Navigation
│   │   │   └── hooks/      # Custom hooks
│   │   ├── app.json        # Expo config
│   │   └── package.json
│   │
│   └── web/                # Next.js app (Desktop browsers)
│       ├── app/            # Next.js App Router
│       ├── src/
│       │   ├── components/ # Web components
│       │   └── hooks/     # Custom hooks
│       └── public/         # Static assets
│
├── docs/                   # Documentation
├── rebuild-roadmap/        # Roadmap & planning
├── package.json            # Root workspace config
└── .cursorrules            # This file
```

**Reference**: `docs/02-mobile/02-architecture.md` and `docs/03-platforms/01-multi-platform-strategy.md` for details

